{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.1","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:1","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.002.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. (2 Pi 2:1-22. Jud 3, etc. Tit 1:10-16.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Sache que, dans les derniers jours, il y aura des temps difficiles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.2","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.2.26","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 2:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.2.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.2","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:2","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Car les hommes seront \u00e9go\u00efstes, amis de l\u2019argent, fanfarons, hautains, blasph\u00e9mateurs, rebelles \u00e0 leurs parents, ingrats, irr\u00e9ligieux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.1","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.3","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:3","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>insensibles, d\u00e9loyaux, calomniateurs, intemp\u00e9rants, cruels, ennemis des gens de bien,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.4","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.2","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.4","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:4","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>tra\u00eetres, emport\u00e9s, enfl\u00e9s d\u2019orgueil, aimant le plaisir plus que Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.5","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.5","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:5","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>ayant l\u2019apparence de la pi\u00e9t\u00e9, mais reniant ce qui en fait la force. \u00c9loigne-toi de ces hommes-l\u00e0.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.6","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.4","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.6","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:6","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il en est parmi eux qui s\u2019introduisent dans les maisons, et qui captivent des femmes d\u2019un esprit faible et born\u00e9, charg\u00e9es de p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, agit\u00e9es par des passions de toute esp\u00e8ce,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.7","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.5","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.7","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:7","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>apprenant toujours et ne pouvant jamais arriver \u00e0 la connaissance de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.8","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.6","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.8","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:8","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>De m\u00eame que Jann\u00e8s et Jambr\u00e8s s\u2019oppos\u00e8rent \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, de m\u00eame ces hommes s\u2019opposent \u00e0 la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, \u00e9tant corrompus d\u2019entendement, r\u00e9prouv\u00e9s en ce qui concerne la foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.9","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.7","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.9","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:9","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mais ils ne feront pas de plus grands progr\u00e8s; car leur folie sera manifeste pour tous, comme le fut celle de ces deux hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.10","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.8","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.10","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:10","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-17: cf. 2 Co 6:3-10. (Ac 13:50; 14:1-22.) 2 Ti 1:13. 2 Pi 1:19-21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Pour toi, tu as suivi de pr\u00e8s mon enseignement, ma conduite, mes r\u00e9solutions, ma foi, ma douceur, ma charit\u00e9, ma constance,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.11","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.9","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.11","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:11","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>mes pers\u00e9cutions, mes souffrances. A quelles souffrances n\u2019ai-je pas \u00e9t\u00e9 expos\u00e9 \u00e0 Antioche, \u00e0 Icone, \u00e0 Lystre? Quelles pers\u00e9cutions n\u2019ai-je pas support\u00e9es? Et le Seigneur m\u2019a d\u00e9livr\u00e9 de toutes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.12","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.10","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.12","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:12","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Or, tous ceux qui veulent vivre pieusement en J\u00e9sus-Christ seront pers\u00e9cut\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.13","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.11","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.13","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:13","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mais les hommes m\u00e9chants et imposteurs avanceront toujours plus dans le mal, \u00e9garant les autres et \u00e9gar\u00e9s eux-m\u00eames.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.14","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.12","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.14","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:14","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Toi, demeure dans les choses que tu as apprises, et reconnues certaines, sachant de qui tu les as apprises;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.15","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.13","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.15","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:15","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>d\u00e8s ton enfance, tu connais les saintes lettres, qui peuvent te rendre sage \u00e0 salut par la foi en J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.16","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.14","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.16","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:16","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Toute \u00c9criture est inspir\u00e9e de Dieu, et utile pour enseigner, pour convaincre, pour corriger, pour instruire dans la justice,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.17","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.15","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.17","label":"","reference":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:17","prev_osis_id":"2Tim.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Tim.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Tim.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>afin que l\u2019homme de Dieu soit accompli et propre \u00e0 toute bonne \u0153uvre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.4.1","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Tim.3.16","name":"2 Timoth\u00e9e 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Tim.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb9dec462.62406887');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af8